==English==

===Noun===
'''order'''
# Arrangement, disposition.
# Good arrangement; opposite to [[chaos]].
# A [[command]].
# A request for some [[product]] or [[service]].
# A religious group.
#  ''Biology.''  In [[animal]] [[taxonomy]], the classification below [[class]] and above [[family]].

